-- Turkey's Bank Asya Q2 net profit tumbles 81 percent
-- By Ceyda Caglayan
-- Tue Aug 12, 2014 01:23AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, Aug 12 (Reuters) - Turkish Islamic lender Bank Asya <ASYAB.IS> posted a net profit of 10.6 million lira ($4.9 million) in the second quarter, sliding 81 percent from a year earlier, it said in a statement to the Istanbul stock exchange late on Monday.

